      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model. The engine and transmission remain functional and steady for daily driving, though potential buyers should expect some noticeable cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior, including various scratches and upholstery aging. It has been maintained to ensure it stays roadworthy, making it a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
