    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and fading clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though the suspension is getting a bit noisy over bumps and it will likely need new tires soon. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its mileage and age.",
